<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/6537806-megasolipsist"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1378520059i/6537806._UY100_CR16,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/6537806-megasolipsist">MegaSolipsist</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">He never said it was geographically disposed towards poverty and backwardness, just that the geography inhibits the spread of domesticated crops that <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">He never said it was geographically disposed towards poverty and backwardness, just that the geography inhibits the spread of domesticated crops that are vital for agriculture and contained much less domestic-able animals than Eurasia, thereby severely limiting the speed of it's development. Two very different things.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
